      <title>花旗集团出售 Maple 债券，这是 2015 年以来首次大规模交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/citigroup-selling-maple-bonds-in-first-sizable-deal-since-2015</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国银行在公布财报后寻求融资多元化，花旗集团近十年来首次在加元债券市场发行大规模债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/citigroup-selling-maple-bonds-in-first-sizable-deal-since-2015</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:13:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
