      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/oil-bounces-off-monthly-low-as-war-risk-keeps-tradders-skittish</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东冲突升级的新迹象有限，油价小幅走低，但由于技术支撑限制了跌幅，油价徘徊在月度低点之上。]]></description>
